<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 18:08:27 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>“令人震惊的新事件”：加沙战争导致意大利反犹太主义袭击大幅增加</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/alarming-and-new-big-spike-in-antisemitic-attacks-in-italy-as-a-result-of-gaza-war/0000018b-aa1d-df89-a79f-bf3f650c0000</link><description>目前针对意大利犹太人的反犹太主义程度可能不像欧洲邻国那样极端，但仍然是前所未有的。犹太社区负责人表示：“我们很担心，但并不害怕”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 17:03:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/alarming-and-new-big-spike-in-antisemitic-attacks-in-italy-as-a-result-of-gaza-war/0000018b-aa1d-df89-a79f-bf3f650c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府不批准在加沙边境附近建设新社区</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-approves-construction-of-new-community-near-gaza-border/0000018b-aa3e-d1c2-a3cf-ba3e7cf30000</link><description>负责规划和建设的委员会批准了在距边境约 7 公里（4.4 英里）处建设社区的计划。尽管有战争和她自己办公室内的反对，环境保护部长西尔曼还是支持了该计划</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 16:25:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israeli-govt-approves-construction-of-new-community-near-gaza-border/0000018b-aa3e-d1c2-a3cf-ba3e7cf30000</guid></item><item><title>网上越来越多地否认哈马斯 10 月 7 日大屠杀</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/denial-of-hamas-october-7-massacre-is-gaining-pace-online/0000018b-aa45-d5aa-a19f-afffabf10000</link><description>随着越来越多的人淡化该恐怖组织对其残酷谋杀、强奸和破坏的责任，否认哈马斯暴行的言论在网上越来越受欢迎</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 15:51:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/denial-of-hamas-october-7-massacre-is-gaining-pace-online/0000018b-aa45-d5aa-a19f-afffabf10000</guid></item><item><title>由于安息日火车运行，以色列的宗教斗争在战争期间暂停</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-religious-battles-on-pause-during-war-as-trains-run-on-shabbat/0000018b-a9e2-d77d-a39b-fde6aeef0000</link><description>随着加沙战争愈演愈烈，以色列关于公共交通的内部斗争逐渐停止，公共汽车、火车和飞机在安息日继续运营。</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 14:57:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-religious-battles-on-pause-during-war-as-trains-run-on-shabbat/0000018b-a9e2-d77d-a39b-fde6aeef0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯以色列议员阿巴斯谴责哈马斯袭击，称大屠杀并不“代表我们的阿拉伯社会”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/arab-list-mk-abbas-denounces-hamas-attack-says-massacre-doesnt-represent-arab-society/0000018b-aa11-d5aa-a19f-affb1b4b0000</link><description>阿拉伯联合名单领导人曼苏尔·阿巴斯在阿拉伯语电台采访中表示，“伊斯兰教的价值观迫使我们不能把妇女、儿童和老人当作俘虏。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 14:36:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/arab-list-mk-abbas-denounces-hamas-attack-says-massacre-doesnt-represent-arab-society/0000018b-aa11-d5aa-a19f-affb1b4b0000</guid></item><item><title>公务员制度委员会调查政府雇员撰写一系列批评内塔尼亚胡的《国土报》文章</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/govt-employee-investigated-for-writing-series-of-haaretz-articles-critical-of-pm/0000018b-a9c6-d0e2-af8f-f9f789b90000</link><description>精神病学家兼兼职公务员埃兰·罗尔尼克博士因在《国土报》上发表“煽动”反对内塔尼亚胡的专栏文章而受到公务员委员会纪律调查部门的讯问</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 13:23:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/govt-employee-investigated-for-writing-series-of-haaretz-articles-critical-of-pm/0000018b-a9c6-d0e2-af8f-f9f789b90000</guid></item><item><title>“巴勒斯坦人对以色列人抱有一种道德至上的感觉”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinians-live-with-a-feeling-of-moral-supremacy-over-israelis/0000018b-a542-dc0b-a1cb-e5c655640000</link><description>东耶路撒冷的巴勒斯坦人应对 10 月 7 日大屠杀的一种方式是相信为哈马斯开脱的阴谋论。一位专家表示，“巴勒斯坦人一直是受害者，但仅仅一天之内，他们就变成了施害者——他们不知道如何处理这一点”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 13:08:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article-magazine/.premium/palestinians-live-with-a-feeling-of-moral-supremacy-over-israelis/0000018b-a542-dc0b-a1cb-e5c655640000</guid></item><item><title>当哈马斯 10 月 7 日试图杀害我的孩子时，他们知道加沙接下来会发生什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/hamas-tried-to-kill-my-children-on-october-7-it-knew-what-would-happen-next-in-gaza/0000018b-a985-d530-a5df-e9efc0e40000</link><description>当哈马斯恐怖分子上个月袭击以色列南部的基布兹时，该组织知道以色列将不得不全力报复。他们认为，为了谋杀以色列平民的快乐，数千名无辜加沙人的死亡是值得付出的代价</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 13:04:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/hamas-tried-to-kill-my-children-on-october-7-it-knew-what-would-happen-next-in-gaza/0000018b-a985-d530-a5df-e9efc0e40000</guid></item><item><title>支持比比的报纸改变态度并要求他在战争结束后辞职</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/pro-bibi-newspaper-changes-tune-and-calls-for-his-resignation-after-war-ends/0000018b-a96a-dc41-af9f-eb6a2a5a0000</link><description>历来支持内塔尼亚胡的报纸《以色列报》谴责总理的“政治争吵”，并宣称他应该下台。 “不要再到处指责，承担起责任，接受责任在你身上。”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 11:47:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/pro-bibi-newspaper-changes-tune-and-calls-for-his-resignation-after-war-ends/0000018b-a96a-dc41-af9f-eb6a2a5a0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列母亲愿意成为哈马斯人质与女儿团聚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/mother-of-two-kidnapped-children-willing-to-be-hostage-243-to-see-her-daughters-again/0000018b-a91e-dc41-af9f-eb3e2b5f0000</link><description>Maayan Zin 是 15 岁达芙娜和 8 岁艾拉的母亲，她呼吁内塔尼亚胡和拜登带女儿回家。 “如果你现在不能带回我的女儿们……我求你了，带我去找她们吧”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 10:40:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/mother-of-two-kidnapped-children-willing-to-be-hostage-243-to-see-her-daughters-again/0000018b-a91e-dc41-af9f-eb3e2b5f0000</guid></item><item><title>美国和以色列在加沙战争问题上的利益分歧迫在眉睫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-and-israels-looming-divergence-of-interests-over-the-gaza-war/0000018b-a917-d15f-a3db-bfd75d390000</link><description>尽管美国总统乔·拜登一直坚定支持以色列，但他将无法忽视党内对以色列在加沙地带的做法日益批评的声音</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 10:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/the-u-s-and-israels-looming-divergence-of-interests-over-the-gaza-war/0000018b-a917-d15f-a3db-bfd75d390000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩向以色列发射20枚火箭弹，以色列国防军以炮火还击；加沙火箭袭击以色列南部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article-live/pm-no-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages-jewish-man-killed-at-la-protest/0000018b-a7f5-dc0b-a1cb-e7f72f5d0000</link><description>以色列各地举行纪念活动，纪念袭击发生一个月 ■ 加兰特表示，战后以色列将在加沙享有充分的行动自由 ■ 10 月 7 日，哈马斯屠杀中至少有 1,300 名平民和士兵丧生，其中 241 名人质在加沙被扣，40 人下落不明■ 哈马斯控制的加沙卫生部：超过10,000人死亡</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 09:44:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article-live/pm-no-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages-jewish-man-killed-at-la-protest/0000018b-a7f5-dc0b-a1cb-e7f72f5d0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列政府改变了在战争期间冻结信息自由请求的意图</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/government-backtracks-on-intention-to-freeze-freedom-of-information-requests-during-war/0000018b-a8e6-d9c0-a5fb-e9fe71f20000</link><description>在公众压力和非政府组织的努力下，政府表示信息自由请求将正常处理，尽管之前由于持续的战争而出现延误</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 09:33:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/government-backtracks-on-intention-to-freeze-freedom-of-information-requests-during-war/0000018b-a8e6-d9c0-a5fb-e9fe71f20000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡向美国广播公司新闻表示：如果不释放以色列人质，加沙就不会停火</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-abc-news-no-gaza-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018b-a87b-dc41-af9f-eb7b0e760000</link><description>当被问及他是否认为自己应该为以色列因哈马斯的袭击而措手不及承担责任时，内塔尼亚胡回答说：“当然。”这不是一个问题。战争结束后就会解决”</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 07:59:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-to-abc-news-no-gaza-ceasefire-without-release-of-israeli-hostages/0000018b-a87b-dc41-af9f-eb7b0e760000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队抵达加沙心脏地带，瞄准哈马斯最后的防御工事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-reaches-the-heart-of-gaza-and-takes-aim-at-hamas-final-defenses/0000018b-a67a-dc0b-a1cb-e7fe227a0000</link><description>以色列国防军已经包围了加沙城，哈马斯似乎没有任何真正的能力阻止以色列装甲部队的前进 ■ 真主党不再躲在黎巴嫩的哈马斯部队后面 ■ 哈马斯对加沙边境社区的袭击改变了以色列公众的秩序焦虑</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 04:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-army-reaches-the-heart-of-gaza-and-takes-aim-at-hamas-final-defenses/0000018b-a67a-dc0b-a1cb-e7fe227a0000</guid></item><item><title>国土报卡通</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-07/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-a6a2-d9c0-a5fb-effa72810000</link><description></description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 03:59:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/daily-cartoon/2023-11-07/ty-article-opinion/haaretz-cartoon/0000018b-a6a2-d9c0-a5fb-effa72810000</guid></item><item><title>犹太男子在洛杉矶附近亲巴勒斯坦集会的“争吵”中被杀，可能是仇恨犯罪</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-man-killed-in-altercation-at-pro-palestinian-rally-near-la-in-possible-hate-crime/0000018b-a7ce-d9c0-a5fb-efde872e0000</link><description>据警方称，69 岁的保罗·凯斯勒 (Paul Kessler) 与一名亲巴勒斯坦示威者发生口角，警方将这起事件视为凶杀案</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 03:34:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/jewish-man-killed-in-altercation-at-pro-palestinian-rally-near-la-in-possible-hate-crime/0000018b-a7ce-d9c0-a5fb-efde872e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列缺乏退出计划正在考验美国的耐心</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-lack-of-an-exit-plan-is-testing-american-patience/0000018b-a6ac-d9c0-a5fb-effc8f5f0000</link><description>美国在也门的立场以及在阿富汗和伊拉克的历史告诉它，过多的耐心是一个战略错误；如果没有明确的退出计划，以色列可能会发现自己被排除在外</description><pubDate>Tue, 07 Nov 2023 03:08:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-07/ty-article/.premium/israels-lack-of-an-exit-plan-is-testing-american-patience/0000018b-a6ac-d9c0-a5fb-effc8f5f0000</guid></item><item><title>离开吧，内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-07/ty-article-opinion/just-leave-netanyahu/0000018b-a688-dc41-af9f-efaa8a040000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 22:05:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/editorial/2023-11-07/ty-article-opinion/just-leave-netanyahu/0000018b-a688-dc41-af9f-efaa8a040000</guid></item><item><title>“内塔尼亚胡的双手沾满了我家人的鲜血”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-familys-blood-is-on-netanyahus-hands/0000018b-a633-dc41-af9f-ef33c9170000</link><description></description><pubDate>Mon, 06 Nov 2023 21:53:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-06/ty-article-opinion/.premium/my-familys-blood-is-on-netanyahus-hands/0000018b-a633-dc41-af9f-ef33c9170000</guid></item></channel></rss>